04-15T11:20:00.000Z","msg":"根據這項新研究，武漢病毒與 HIV 之間存在一個主要區別。愛滋病毒可以在 T 細胞中複製，同時不斷產生更多的複製 HIV 病毒來感染其他細胞。但是這項研究的科學家發現，武漢病毒在進入 T 細胞後並未觀察到冠狀病毒的任何生長； 武漢病毒和 T 細胞可能最終一起死亡。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-15T11:38:41.000Z","msg":"suicide bombing <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 屌你重唔認係人造"},{"pid":"3b81f561c5e0c0bde19ce203cec46b22d16fadae","tid":1973742,"uid":33263,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"e71578bee1e14916f1ac3f4039afc801b5986fd1","tid":1973742,"uid":175036,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-15T11:35:08.000Z","msg":"係嘅邊有咁多人好得返<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-15T11:39:05.000Z","msg":"因為事實上 係唔會好返"},{"pid":"9dcde8cc811545f482677aa7cbcbcfd6a0f4f0d2","tid":1973742,"uid":149978,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"4d2fc228a2d83e24e61e4013998e46dca007453a","tid":1973742,"uid":17103,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"eedcc51810cb7efedd892716d9d2754cea580bec","tid":1973742,"uid":149978,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"6f14ac9f5f500ad104f87ab0010d54f4ba9eb203","tid":1973742,"uid":33874,"like":31,"dislike":35,"score":-4,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-04-15T11:15:01.000Z","msg":"下？ T virus?<br />\n咁要搵Leon"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-15T11:20:00.000Z","msg":"根據這項新研究，武漢病毒與 HIV 之間存在一個主要區別。愛滋病毒可以在 T 細胞中複製，同時不斷產生更多的複製 HIV 病毒來感染其他細胞。但是這項研究的科學家發現，武漢病毒在進入 T 細胞後並未觀察到冠狀病毒的任何生長； 武漢病毒和 T 細胞可能最終一起死亡。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-15T11:38:41.000Z","msg":"suicide bombing <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 屌你重唔認係人造"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-15T11:48:00.000Z","msg":"武漢肺炎病毒到底從哪來？<br />\n<br />\n本文略長，重點如下：<br />\nWARS 在雲南找到最近親戚，兩者非常相似。（比 SARS 近得多）<br />\nWARS 的中間宿主尚未確認，但現有和蛇有關的分析完全是錯誤的。<br />\n仔細檢視後，WARS 的 S蛋白質變異和 HIV 毫無任何關係。（該論文已由作者撤稿）<br />\n沒有可靠證據支持現有的陰謀論，WARS 極可能是自然演化而來的病毒。<br />\n現階段出現一些搶快不可靠的研究，即使同儕審查過的論文也不可盡信。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://pansci.asia/archives/178842\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpansci.asia%2Farchives%2F178842&d=kRIfmd%2Br1GQrfPRU1wEKQLnp9gp%2BSvHPFRLSSJzTNPo%3D&h=448bac1d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://pansci.asia/archives/178842</a>"},{"pid":"95d365fb0ef91bfd053cde9c8e2e2f3422483abc","tid":1973742,"uid":341865,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-15T11:48:52.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">Source呢屌你老母content farm狗</span>"},{"pid":"52ea4391db45fc7e827b7143d03b181e88f535e0","tid":1973742,"uid":251732,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"af8ea7c385d1c5babdd075ec01289306c7fca864","tid":1973742,"uid":76310,"like":22,"dislike":1,"score":21,"quote":{"pid":"bb2b7b7edddfcfb39f655ba54b606a54299f7f1b","tid":1973742,"uid":149978,"like":48,"dislike":2,"score":46,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-04-15T11:17:13.000Z","msg":"咁點解有咁多患者會好得返。<br />\nHIV好似中左招個個幾乎無一倖免。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-15T11:22:24.000Z","msg":"好番既人<br />\n隨時病毒潛伏在體內咋"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-15T11:50:12.000Z","msg":"唔keep住食藥實死<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bfa65e5c369950feea261e12190d23079474ae0f","tid":1973742,"uid":207197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-15T11:50:12.000Z","msg":"中國解放軍研究<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd4334cc17ed8eec5f05a649e73251ec706a0b65","tid":1973742,"uid":80153,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-15T11:50:34.000Z","msg":"其實係咪唔會好返<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e36370388f809eb9541cfaa0de32f7ad8ffefcfc","tid":1973742,"uid":293227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-15T11:51:43.000Z","msg":"癲"},{"pid":"46ba58ce27b1456a7dbf30c3a4007383c1f46ef4","tid":1973742,"uid":149978,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"9dcde8cc811545f482677aa7cbcbcfd6a0f4f0d2","tid":1973742,"uid":149978,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"4d2fc228a2d83e24e61e4013998e46dca007453a","tid":1973742,"uid":17103,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"eedcc51810cb7efedd892716d9d2754cea580bec","tid":1973742,"uid":149978,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-15T11:20:00.000Z","msg":"根據這項新研究，武漢病毒與 HIV 之間存在一個主要區別。愛滋病毒可以在 T 細胞中複製，同時不斷產生更多的複製 HIV 病毒來感染其他細胞。但是這項研究的科學家發現，武漢病毒在進入 T 細胞後並未觀察到冠狀病毒的任何生長； 武漢病毒和 T 細胞可能最終一起死亡。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-15T11:38:41.000Z","msg":"suicide bombing <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 屌你重唔認係人造"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-15T11:48:00.000Z","msg":"武漢肺炎病毒到底從哪來？<br />\n<br />\n本文略長，重點如下：<br />\nWARS 在雲南找到最近親戚，兩者非常相似。（比 SARS 近得多）<br />\nWARS 的中間宿主尚未確認，但現有和蛇有關的分析完全是錯誤的。<br />\n仔細檢視後，WARS 的 S蛋白質變異和 HIV 毫無任何關係。（該論文已由作者撤稿）<br />\n沒有可靠證據支持現有的陰謀論，WARS 極可能是自然演化而來的病毒。<br />\n現階段出現一些搶快不可靠的研究，即使同儕審查過的論文也不可盡信。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://pansci.asia/archives/178842\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpansci.asia%2Farchives%2F178842&d=kRIfmd%2Br1GQrfPRU1wEKQLnp9gp%2BSvHPFRLSSJzTNPo%3D&h=448bac1d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://pansci.asia/archives/178842</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-15T11:52:17.000Z","msg":"然而，與目前更加明確的線索相比，並不需要這些陰謀論解釋 WARS 的起源。這次疫情中國政府沒有說實話、中國在歐美有間諜活動、之前處理實驗不夠謹慎讓 SARS 外洩過，這些都是事實，也無法排除中國私下研發生物武器的可能性。但是要證明 WARS 和中國研發生物武器有關係，目前沒有合理的證據。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>反倒有更強力的證據指出，WARS 就是另一場源於自然的智人危機。</strong><br />\n<br />\nWARS 和最近親戚分家後，才獲得跨物種感染力。<br />\n<br />\n華盛頓大學的 Trevor Bedford 根據序列差異，估計雲南的 RaTG13 和武漢的 WARS 分家的年代，介於 25 到 65 年前；此一數字會受到突變率與宿主影響（提醒一下，我們仍然不知道 WARS 的原始宿主是哪種動物）。不過大概可以確定，兩者分家雖然不是太久，卻也已經有一段時間，不像是最近幾年的事。"},{"pid":"fd95ab5c0